=============================================================================================================
                                     RELAXATION SETTINGS
=============================================================================================================
JOBT  20       job type: structure relaxation (20)
NPAR  4        number of cores for parallel run
NDIM  3        dimensionality of unit cell: crystal (3); cluster (0)
MITR  100      maximum number of cell optimization steps
RLXT  3        cell optimization type: force only (2); full cell (3); volume (7)
PGPA  0.0      external pressure in GPa
ETOL  1e-8     error tolerance for cell optimization convergence
COUT  12       output options: E (00) final; (01) first/final; (02) all steps; 
               EF (10) final; (11) first/final; (12) all steps;
MINT  0        minimizer type: (0) BFGS2; (1) CG-FR; (2) CG-PR; (3) steepest descent;
=============================================================================================================
